channel.description:
I've been coding lately, and suddenly, people started complaining about my bank. They said they can't use quickly bank and I tried to do it, but it didn't work either. If someone can give me a case of the quickly bank or a code for quickly bank, please post it. I really need it and I'll appreciate it.
BTW, for fight caves can someone give me the name and the order of the monsters?
